quran[67]{c,v,t}:
  90,1,Ndahiriye kuri uyu mujyi (wa Maka)
  90,2,No kuri wowe (Ntumwa Muhamadi) utuye uyu mujyi
  90,3,No ku mubyeyi (Adamu) n’abo yabyaye
  90,4,"Mu by’ukuri, twaremye umuntu kugira ngo (abeho) mu ngorane"
  90,5,Ese akeka ko nta n’umwe wamushobora
  90,6,"Aravuga ati \"Nakoresheje umutungo mwinshi"
  90,7,Ese akeka ko nta n’umwe umubona
  90,8,Ese ntitwamuhaye amaso abiri
  90,9,Ndetse n’ururimi n’iminwa ibiri
  90,10,Tukanamwereka inzira ebyiri (iy’icyiza n’ikibi)
  90,11,Ariko ntiyigeze ashaka kunyura mu nzira igoranye (iganisha ku byiza n’intsinzi)
  90,12,Ese ni iki cyakumenyesha iyo nzira igoranye
  90,13,(Ni) ukubohora umucakara
  90,14,Cyangwa gutanga amafunguro ku munsi w’amapfa
  90,15,(Ayo mafunguro ukayaha) imfubyi mufitanye isano rya bugufi
  90,16,Cyangwa umukene (uryamye) mu ivumbi (uri mu kaga)
  90,17,"Hanyuma akaba umwe mu bemeramana, bakanagirana inama zo kwihangana ndetse bakanagirana inama zo kugira impuhwe"
  90,18,Abo ni abo mu kuboko kw’iburyo (mu Ijuru)
  90,19,"Naho abahakanye amagambo yacu, ni abo mu kuboko kw’ibumoso (mu muriro)"
  90,20,Bazaba bafungiranye mu muriro (badafite aho binjirira n’aho basohokera)
  91,1,Ndahiriye ku izuba n’urumuri rwaryo
  91,2,No ku kwezi igihe kurikurikiye
  91,3,No ku manywa igihe agaragaje urumuri (rw’izuba)
  91,4,No ku ijoro igihe riritwikiriye
  91,5,No ku kirere ndetse n’uwagihanze
  91,6,No ku isi n’uwayirambuye
  91,7,No kuri roho n’uwayitunganyije
  91,8,Hanyuma akayigaragariza ikibi n’icyiza
  91,9,"Mu by’ukuri, uweza roho ye (akubaha Allah kandi agakora ibikorwa byiza) yaratsinze"
  91,10,Kandi rwose uwatereranye roho ye ari mu gihombo
  91,11,Abantu ba Thamudu bahinyuye (Intumwa yabo) kubera kwigomeka
  91,12,Ubwo ubarusha ububi yahagurukanaga ibakwe (akajya kwica ingamiya y’imbyeyi)
  91,13,"Nuko Intumwa ya Allah (Swaleh) irababwira iti \"Iyo ni ingamiya ya Allah (ntimuyigirire nabi), kandi ntimuyibuze gushoka"
  91,14,"Ariko baramuhinyuye (ya ngamiya) barayica. Nuko Nyagasani wabo arabarimbura ku bw’icyaha cyabo, ndetse bose abarimbura mu buryo bureshya (baba abakuru n’abato, abakire n’abakene, ndetse n’abakomeye n’abaciriritse)"
  91,15,Kandi (Allah) ntatinya ingaruka zabyo
  92,1,Ndahiriye ku ijoro igihe riguye
  92,2,No ku manywa igihe atangaje
  92,3,No ku waremye ikigabo n’ikigore
  92,4,"Mu by’ukuri, ibikorwa byanyu biratandukanye"
  92,5,Wawundi utanga (amaturo) akanatinya (Allah)
  92,6,Kandi akizera icyiza (Ijuru)
  92,7,Tuzamworohereza inzira y’ibyiza
  92,8,"Ariko uzaba umunyabugugu, akirata yumva ko (yishoboye)"
  92,9,Akanahinyura icyiza
  92,10,Tuzamworohereza inzira y’ibibi
  92,11,"Kandi ubwo azaba arimbuka (ajyanywe mu muriro), umutungo we ntacyo uzamumarira"
  92,12,"Mu by’ukuri, ukuyobora ni ukwacu"
  92,13,"Kandi mu by’ukuri, ni na twe tugenga iby’imperuka n’ibibanza (iby’isi)"
  92,14,"Bityo, mbaburiye umuriro ugurumana"
  92,15,Ntawe uzawinjiramo utari inkozi y’ibibi
  92,16,Wawundi wahinyuye (ukuri) akanagutera umugongo
  92,17,"Ariko ukora ibikorwa byiza, azawurindwa"
  92,18,Wawundi utanga umutungo we kugira ngo yiyeze
  92,19,Kandi ntashishikazwe no kwiturwa n’uwo yagiriye neza
  92,20,"Ahubwo (akabikora agamije) gushaka kwishimirwa na Nyagasani we, Uwikirenga"
  92,21,Kandi rwose azishima (ubwo azinjira mu Ijuru)
  93,1,Ndahiriye ku gasusuruko
  93,2,No ku ijoro igihe ryijimye
  93,3,"(Yewe Muhamadi), Nyagasani wawe ntiyagutereranye kandi nta n’ubwo yakurakariye"
  93,4,Kandi rwose ubuzima bw’imperuka ni bwo bwiza kuri wowe kurusha ububanza (ubw’isi)
  93,5,"Mu by’ukuri, bidatinze Nyagasani wawe azaguha kandi uzishima"
  93,6,Ese ntiyagusanze uri imfubyi akaguha icumbi (abakwitaho)
  93,7,"Akanagusanga udasobanukiwe (Qur’an n’amategeko yayo), nuko akakuyobora"
  93,8,Akaba yaranagusanze uri umukene maze akagukungahaza (akaguha kunyurwa)
  93,9,"Bityo, ntugahutaze imfubyi"
  93,10,Ntukanakankamire uje asaba
  93,11,"Kandi ingabire za Nyagasani wawe (yaguhaye), ujye uzigaragaza (umushimira)"